CompanyDescription.label: Company Description
CompanyDescription.value: Bank7 Corp is a United States-based bank holding company. The company offers deposit banking products, including commercial deposit services, commercial checking, money market, and other deposit accounts, retail deposit services such as certificates of deposit, money market accounts, checking accounts, negotiable order of withdrawal accounts, savings accounts, and automated teller machine access. The bank generates its revenue in the form of interest income.
